# Type: Short summary in present tense (max ~72 chars)
# Types: Feat | Fix | Chore | Refactor | Docs | Test | Update
#
# - Brief description of change 1 in present tense
# - Brief description of change 2 in present tense
#
# Rules enforced by commitlint:
#   • Header must match  "Type: Summary"
#   • Body must not be empty
#   • Every body line must start with "- "
#   • Summary and type must not be empty
# Lines starting with "#" are ignored.
